Date: 1995-05-02

Title: Determinant of twisted chiral Dirac Operator on the Lattice

Authors: C. D. Fosco and S. Randjbar-Daemi

Comments: 9 pages, no figures. Error in the derivation of the non-holomorphic

piece correctedJournal-ref: Phys.Lett. B354 (1995) 383-388

Using the overlap formulation, we calculate the fermionic determinant on thelattice for chiral fermions with twisted boundary conditions in two dimensions.When the lattice spacing tends to zero we recover the results of the usualstring-theory continuum calculations.